Perceptor::

Perceptor heard the tape and told to Bullet "Bullet, you're in jaws 
for many reasons: one. Chamaleon is an important assistan of 
Darkfate, the first in rank... two. Chamaleon doesn't have acces to 
any information. three. Darkfate is tired to have this sort of events 
inside his base."

Perceptor added "my work, by now, it's find out what happened... It's 
the master who is going to decide your punishment - Darkfate could be 
indulgent this time, but if you're involved in other event like this 
I coudn't be sure what will happen next; you really promised to be a 
great predacon... but if you don't learn how hold yours circuits, one 
of those days you will do something that you will regret it 
someday..."

"By now, I can't give you access to most of areas of the base -but I  
have to have a regist of every bot here " said Perceptor while he 
pressed a button and the layer moved showing a black surface"Put one 
of your hands in the surface" said Perceptor "that surface will take 
your signal signature"

"By now, I think that you should check your circuits -Thyphon's 
poyson it's very dangerous and after that go to rest" said the 
male "Also, let be alone Chameleon, if anyone of this Fortres annoy 
him, he or she will have a lot troubles with the Leader"

Perceptor fell in silence waitting Bullet reaction... but still he 
had several things to tell him
